3. Visual Variant System

The Stitch export provides three visual variants for all four screens. The underlying HTML structure and component hierarchy are identical across variants — only design tokens (colours, effects, backgrounds) change.

Variant	Background	Cards	Key Differentiators
Dark v1	#111418 solid	#1E2228 solid	Solid card backgrounds, strong card-shadow, border-gray-800 on all cards
Dark v2	#111418 gradient	Glassmorphism	Backdrop-blur header & bottom nav, floating bottom nav bar added, gradient avatar ring
Light	#FFFFFF / white	white + shadow	Text colours inverted (gray-800), Inter font explicit, green positive indicators darker (green-600)

Recommendation: Ship Dark v2 as the primary production theme. Expose a system-preference toggle (prefers-color-scheme) to switch to the Light variant. Dark v1 can be deprecated after the glassmorphism system is validated.



